1. *Silu* smo primenili kako bismo postigli željeni efekat. (We applied *silu* to achieve the desired effect.)
2. Njegova *silovitost* je bila zastrašujuća. (His *forcefulness* was frightening.)
3. Čovek je *silom* pokušao da otme novčanik starici. (The man tried to snatch the purse from the old lady *by force*.)
4. Oni su *silom prilika* morali da se razdvoje. (They had to separate *by force of circumstances*.)
5. *Siluje* me miris cveća u proleće. (The scent of flowers in spring *overwhelms* me.)
6. Ona je bila *silovana* pre nekoliko godina. (She was *raped* a few years ago.)
7. Odlučili su da *silom* zatvore vrata kako bi sprečili dalje širenje požara. (They decided to *forcefully* close the doors to prevent further spread of the fire.)
8. *Sila* gravitacije je ono što nas drži na Zemlji. (The *force* of gravity is what keeps us on Earth.)
9. Zbog *sile okolnosti* morao sam otkazati putovanje. (Due to *circumstances beyond my control*, I had to cancel the trip.)
10. *Siloviti* vetar je oborio stablo. (The *powerful* wind knocked down the tree.)